resources.description: GGI is traded in the Saudi Exchange. This Open Data is about the historical prices sample of Gulf General Cooperative Insurance Company for the first half of 2023 (from 26 January, 2023 until 22 June, 2023) based on the published information from https://www.saudiexchange.sa/. It includes stock behavior such as Opening Price, Highest, Lowest, Closing Price, Change, Value Traded, and Number of Trades.
resources.name: GGI Share Prices History in Saudi Exchange
